org.wso2.transport.http.netty.internal.websocket

Class WebSocketSessionAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.transport.http.netty.internal.websocket.WebSocketSessionAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, javax.websocket.Session
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultWebSocketSession

    public class WebSocketSessionAdapter
extends Object
implements javax.websocket.Session
    This is the adapter for Session implementation. This is the implementation class of Session interface. In here all overridden methods are unsupported. Then user needs to extend this adapter class and override the methods of this as needed. So only the needed methods from this class are implemented and other methods are automatically unsupported.
